commands to view and generate API keys (since the after the restart of containers it is not valid anymore to aut generate new ones)

Generate a new API key:
docker-compose exec -T app npm run setup-apikeys -- "default-client" 2>&1

Print API keys already stored (shows api_key UUIDs):
docker exec -it user_management_db psql -U postgres -d user_management_db \
  -c "select api_key, client_name, is_active, created_at, last_used from api_keys order by created_at desc limit 20;"
